#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Today's topic is about managing stress.\n"
"\n"
"We know how stressful it is to bring up teenagers in these times. Learning to manage your stress helps you ‚Äì and your family."
msgstr ""
"Isihloko sanamhlanje simalunga nokulawula uxinzelelo.\n"
"\n"
"Siyayazi kunzima kangakanani na ukukhulisa abantwana abafikisayo kula amaxesha. Ukufunda ukulawula uxinzelelo lwakho kunceda wena - kunye nosapho lwakho."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Can managing stress help you and your family? Tap play to find out"
msgstr "Ingaba ukulawula uxinzelelo kungakunceda wena nosapho lwakho? Cofa udlala ukufumanisa"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Greetings everyone.\n"
"\n"
"Today's topic is managing stress.\n"
"\n"
"It is important to know how to manage our stress. At times our children can behave in ways that make us feel stressed and us as parents can make our children feel stressed too.\n"
"\n"
"So, it is important to notice when we feel stressed and take a pause and breathe. That will help you manage your stress."
msgstr ""
"Molweni nonke. \n"
"\n"
"Isihloko sanamhlanje kukulawula uxinzelelo. \n"
"\n"
"Kubalulekile ukwazi indlela yokulawula uxinzelelo lwethu. Ngamanye amaxesha abantwana bethu bangaziphatha ngeendlela ezinokusenza sizive sinoxinzelelo yaye nathi bazali sinokwenza abantwana bethu bazive benonxinzelelo nabo. \n"
"\n"
"Ngoko, kubalulekile ukuqaphela xa siziva sinoxinzelelo kwaye sime siphefumle. Loo nto iya kunceda ulawule uxinzelelo."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"With a few small changes, you can feel more peaceful in your normal day-to-day life.\n"
"\n"
"When you are peaceful, your family members will get calmer too!"
msgstr ""
"Kutshintsho oluncinci, ungaziva unoxolo ngakumbi kubomi bakho besiqhelo bemihla ngemihla.\n"
"\n"
"Xa unoxolo, nosapho lwakho luyazola!"

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.media_female_4.name should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Pause, take a breath. Now hear how taking a simple pause helped @data.characters.media_female_4.name and her teens"
msgstr "Yima, phefumla. Ngoku mamela ukuba ukuma ithutyana kunceda njani u@data.characters.media_female_4.name kunye nabantwana bakhe abafikisayo"

#. type=data_list
#. The string @global.app_name, should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Life is tough sometimes. Before I joined @global.app_name, I used to be grumpy at all times. I would take out my anger on everyone at home, not only my teens but even my husband as well. They would run away when I came home because they knew I would start yelling at them.\n"
"\n"
"Learning to take a pause and breathe was difficult at first. But every time I tried it, it helped me to calm down. Now my teens are no longer running away when I come home and they actually listen better than when I used to shout at them!"
msgstr ""
"Ubomi bunzima ngamanye amaxesha. Phambi kokuba ndizibandakanye kwi @global.app_name, bendihlala ndinengcwangu ngalo lonke ixesha. Bendikhuphela umsindo wam kumntu wonke osekhayeni, ibingengobantwana bam bodwa kodwa nomyeni wam. Babebalekela kude xa ndifika ekhayeni kuba babeyazi ndizakubangxolisa.\n"
"\n"
"Ukufunda ukuma kwaye ndiphefumle bekunzima ekuqaleni. Kodwa ngalo lonke ixesha ndizama, yandinceda ndehlisa umoya. Ngoku abantwana bam abasabalekeli kude xa ndifika ekhayeni kwaye bamamela ngcono kunangexesha bendithethela phezulu nabo!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Let‚Äôs look at an example of how stress can sometimes just get too much, for all of us:"
msgstr "Makhe sijonge indlela uxinezeleko olunokuthi maxa wambi lube ngaphaya kwamandla, kuthi sonke:"

#. type=data_list
#. The following strings should not be translated: 
#.      @data.characters.f1_father.name
#.      @data.characters.f1_son_18.name
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "@data.characters.f1_father.name lost his job. He was sitting at home feeling frustrated and stressed when @data.characters.f1_son_18.name entered the room."
msgstr "u@data.characters.f1_father.name uphelelwe ngumsebenzi. Ebehleli endlini eziva ekhathazekile kwaye enoxinzelelo xa u@data.characters.f1_son_18.name engena egumbini."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Leave me alone and mind your own business!"
msgstr "Yohlukana nam kwaye hoya umsebenzi wakho!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "What did I do? You never listen!"
msgstr "Yintoni endiyenzileyo? Zange wamamela!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "I said leave me alone or you will get a beating!"
msgstr "Ndithe yohlukana nam okanye uzakubethwa!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Look! I have made a house!"
msgstr "Jonga! Ndenze indlu!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Who cares about your stupid house!"
msgstr "Ngubani oyikhathaleleyo londlu yobudenge yakho!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Let's think about what happened in this story."
msgstr "Makhe sicinge ngokwenzekileyo kweli bali."

#. type=data_list
#. The following strings should not be translated: 
#.      @data.characters.f1_father.name's
#.      @data.characters.f1_son_18.name,
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "How do you think @data.characters.f1_father.name's son, @data.characters.f1_son_18.name, felt?"
msgstr "Ucinga ukuba unyana ka@data.characters.f1_father.name, u@data.characters.f1_son_18.name waziva njani?"

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f1_father.name, should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Yes, he did not understand why his father, @data.characters.f1_father.name, got angry, and probably felt all these emotions."
msgstr "Ewe, khange ayiqonde ukuba kutheni utata wakhe, u@data.characters.f1_father.name, wabanomsindo, kwaye azive zonke ezimvakalelo."

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f1_father.name? should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "And @data.characters.f1_father.name?"
msgstr "Kwaye @data.characters.f1_father.name?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Sad"
msgstr "Ulusizi"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Scared"
msgstr "Uyoyika"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Confused"
msgstr "Ubhidekile"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Angry"
msgstr "Unomsindo"

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f1_father.name should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Exactly. @data.characters.f1_father.name was in a difficult situation and this argument only made things worse."
msgstr "Ngokwenene. @data.characters.f1_father.name wayekwimeko enzima kwaye oluxambuliswano lwenza izinto zanzima ngakumbi."

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f1_father.name should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "What could @data.characters.f1_father.name have done differently?"
msgstr "Yintoni @data.characters.f1_father.name ngeyenze ngokwahlukileyo?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Recognise why he felt stressed"
msgstr "Qaphela ukuba kutheni ezive enoxinzelelo"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Yes, when we recognise we feel stressed, we can take a deep breath and respond with calm and understanding. That way we can find solutions together that work."
msgstr "Ewe, xa siziqaphela ukuba siziva sinoxinzelelo, singaphefumla ngokunzulu kwaye siphendule zolileyo nangokuqonda. Ngalondlela singafumana izisombululo ezinokusisebenzela sonke."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Take a deep breath and speak calmly"
msgstr "Phefumla ngokunzulu kwaye uthethe ngokuzolileyo"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Show he understands his teen's feelings"
msgstr "Ubonise ukuba uyayiqonda indlela aziva ngayo umntwana wakhe ofikisayo"

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f1_son_18.name should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Think about solutions together with @data.characters.f1_son_18.name"
msgstr "Cinga ngezisombulululo kunye no@data.characters.f1_son_18.name"

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f1_son_18.name should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Do something positive together with @data.characters.f1_son_18.name"
msgstr "Yenza into elungileyo kunye no@data.characters.f1_son_18.name"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Yes, when we recognise we feel stressed, we can take a deep breath and respond with calm and understanding. That way we can find solutions together that make everyone feel better."
msgstr "Ewe, xa siziqaphela ukuba siziva sinoxinzelelo, singaphefumla ngokunzulu kwaye siphendule zolileyo nangokuqonda. Ngalondlela singafumana izisombululo ezinokusisebenzela sonke."

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f1_father.name should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Thank you for thinking along! Let‚Äôs go back in time and see what @data.characters.f1_father.name does now:"
msgstr "Enkosi ngokucinga kunye! Masibuyele emva ngexesha kwaye sibone ukuba u@data.characters.f1_father.name wenzani ngoku:"

#. type=data_list
#. The following strings should not be translated: 
#.      @data.characters.f1_father.name
#.      @data.characters.f1_son_18.name
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "@data.characters.f1_father.name lost his job. He was sitting at home feeling frustrated and stressed, when his son @data.characters.f1_son_18.name entered the room."
msgstr "u@data.characters.f1_father.name uphelelwe ngumsebenzi. Ebehleli endlini eziva ekhathazekile kwaye enoxinzelelo xa u@data.characters.f1_son_18.name engena egumbini."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Can I have money to buy some airtime?"
msgstr "Ndingakwazi ukufumana imali yokuthenga airtime?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "*(taking a breath)* I‚Äôm sorry son. I had a difficult day today. The boss fired me."
msgstr "*(ephefumlo)* Uxolo nyana. Bendinemini enzima namhlanje. Umphathi wam undigxothile."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Oh no! I need a new school uniform."
msgstr "Oh hayi! Ndidinga impahla entsha yesikolo."

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f1_mother.role_name's should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "I‚Äôll try, son, and your @data.characters.f1_mother.role_name's job will help us get by while I look for another job."
msgstr "Ndizakuzama, nyana, kwaye U@data.characters.f1_mother.role_name umsebenzi wakhe uzokusinceda ngethuba ndisakhangela omnye umsebenzi."

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f1_father.role_name? should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Should I also help you look for work, @data.characters.f1_father.role_name?"
msgstr "Ndingakunceda nam ukukhangela umsebenzi, @data.characters.f1_father.role_name?"

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f1_son_18.name. should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "No it‚Äôs okay, @data.characters.f1_son_18.name. I appreciate your offer. The most important thing is that you work hard at school. Thanks for listening to me."
msgstr "Hayi kulungile, @data.characters.f1_son_18.name. Ndiyakwamkela ukuzinikela kwakho. Eyonanto ibalulekileyo kukuba usebenze nzima esikolweni. Enkosi ngokundimamela."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Let‚Äôs play some soccer together. It will help me get this stress off my mind for a bit."
msgstr "Masidlale ibhola ekhatywayo sobabini. Izakundinceda ndikhuphe uxinzelelo olusengqondweni yam oko mzuzwana."

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f1_father.role_name! should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Okay, @data.characters.f1_father.role_name!"
msgstr "Kulungile, @data.characters.f1_father.role_name!"

#. type=data_list
#. The following strings should not be translated: 
#.      @data.characters.f1_son_18.name
#.      @data.characters.f1_daughter_16.name!
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Now let's look at an example where something simple, like a Safety Word, can help manage stress and keep your teen safe. \n"
"\n"
"First, think back to when you were a teenager. Was there ever a time when you were in danger but you could not tell your family because they would have been angry?\n"
"\n"
"This ALMOST happened to @data.characters.f1_son_18.name and @data.characters.f1_daughter_16.name! Let‚Äôs have a look:"
msgstr ""
"Ngoku masijonge kumzekelo apho kukho into elula, njengeGama eliKhuselekileyo, linganceda ukulawula uxinzelelo kwaye ligcine umntwana wakho ofikisayo ekhuselekile. \n"
"\n"
"Kuqala, cinga emva ngexesha apho wawusengumntwana ofikisayo. Lalikhe lakhona ixesha apho wawusengozini kodwa wawungakwazi ukuxelela usapho lwakho kuba babezakuba nomsindo?\n"
"\n"
"Lento YAPHANTSE ukwenzeka ku@data.characters.f1_son_18.name kunye no@data.characters.f1_daughter_16.name! makhe sijonge:"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Don‚Äôt tell the adults, but I am going to a bar with my friends tonight."
msgstr "Ungabaxeleli abantu abadala, kodwa ndiya emzini othengisa utywala nabahlobo bam ebusuku."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Have fun! I told them I am staying with my girlfriend, but I am actually going to a cool party."
msgstr "Yonwaba! Ndibaxelele ukuba ndihlala nentombi yam endithandana nayo, kodwa apho ndiya khona ndiya epatini."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "I think they are dealing drugs. We could all get arrested. But I can‚Äôt tell my parents ‚Äì they will be so angry!"
msgstr "Ndicinga ukuba basebenzisa iziyobisi. Singabanjwa sonke. Kodwa andinakubaxelela abazali bam ‚Äì baya kuba nomsindo kakhulu!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "I am scared. Everyone is too drunk to drive me home. This guy says he will take me, but he wants us to go to his house first. I can‚Äôt tell my parents ‚Äì I lied about coming to this party."
msgstr "Ndiyoyika. Wonke umntu unxile kakhulu ukuba angandigodusa. Lo mfana uthi angandigodusa, kodwa ufuna siqale kwakhe. Andinakubaxelela abazali bam - ndibaxokisile ngokuza kule pati.‚Äù."

#. type=data_list
#. The following strings should not be translated: 
#.      @data.characters.f1_son_18.name
#.      @data.characters.f1_daughter_16.name
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "These are dangerous situations! Thankfully, @data.characters.f1_son_18.name and @data.characters.f1_daughter_16.name then remembered what their father told them:"
msgstr "Ezi zimeko ezinobungozi! Kungumbulelo,u@data.characters.f1_son_18.name kunye no@data.characters.f1_daughter_16.name baye bakhumbula into utata wabo ewayebaxelele yona:"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"I care about your safety more than anything. If you are ever upset, or scared, you can always call me for help, or tell me about it.\n"
"\n"
"Shall we use an imaginary ‚ÄòAunty Cecilia‚Äô as our Safety Word? Just say something about Aunty Cecilia, I promise that I will try my best to help and I will not be angry ‚Äì even if you are doing something you shouldn't be doing."
msgstr ""
"Ndiyakhathala ngokhuseleko lwakho ngaphezu kwayo nayiphi into. Ukuba uye wakhathazeka, okanye usoyika, ungandifowunela rhoqo malunga noncedo, okanye undixelele ngalonto. \n"
"\n"
"Singasebenzisa umfanekiso ongengowenyani ka 'kaAunty Cecilia' njengeGama loKhuseleko? Itsho nje into malunga noAunt Cecilia, Ndiyathembisa into yokuba ndizakuzama kangangoko ndinako ukunceda kwaye andizukhathazeka -- noba wenza into ongamelanga ukuba uyayenza."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Hey father, how is Aunty Cecilia doing now?"
msgstr "Hey tata, unjani uAunty Cecilia ngoku?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "*(on the other side of the phone)* Not well. We need you at home. I will come pick you up right away. Where are you?"
msgstr "*(Kwelinye icala le phone) * Akukho nto intle. Sidinga wena ekhaya. Ndizazokulanda njengangoku. Uphi?"

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f1_father.role_name should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "(ü§î_thinking_) I think my friends are in trouble. I don‚Äôt want to stop being their friend, but I‚Äôm worried. Maybe @data.characters.f1_father.role_name knows what to do."
msgstr "(ü§î_ ecinga_) Ndicinga abahlobo bam basengxakini. Andifuni ukuyeka ukuba ngumhlobo wabo, kodwa ndikhathazekile. Mhlawumbi u@data.characters.f1_father.role_name uyayazi into amakayenze."

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f1_father.role_name, should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "@data.characters.f1_father.role_name, I just remembered, Aunty Cecilia said she will come visit tomorrow."
msgstr "@data.characters.f1_father.role_name, Ndiye ndakhumbula, Aunty Cecilia wathi uzakuza azokusindwendwela ngomso."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "*(on the other side of the phone)* Okay, I need you at home to help get things ready. I will come pick you up now. Where are you?"
msgstr "*(kwelinye icala le fowuni)* Okay, Ndiyakudinga ekhayeni uzokunceda ukulungisa izinto. Ndizazokulanda ngoku. Uphi?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Having a Safety Word can help your teen stay safe too. You can choose any word as a Safety Word. Only your family knows it means ‚Äòhelp‚Äô.\n"
"\n"
"Your teen can say this word to let you know they are in trouble without you getting angry or punishing them, so you can help them."
msgstr ""
"Ukuba negama elikhuselekileyo kunganceda umntana wakho ofikisayo ahlale ekhuselekile naye. Ungakhetha naliphi igama njengegama elikhuselekileyo. Lusapho lwakho kuphela oluyaziyo ukuba kuthetha 'uncedo'. \n"
"\n"
"Umntana wakho ofikisayo angalibiza eligama ukwazisa ukuba basengxakini ngaphandle kokuba nomsindo okanye ubohlwaye, ke ungakwazi ukubanceda'."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"**What Safety Word can you choose with your teen? Here are some ideas from other families:**\n"
"\n"
