#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Here are a few skills to help you manage stress that you can use with your teens!"
msgstr "Nazi izakhono ezimbalwa ongazisebenzisa ukunceda wena ukwazi ukumelana nonxinzelelo kunye nomntwana wakho ofikisayo!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "BREATHE"
msgstr "PHEFUMLA"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Breathe slowly. Pause.\n"
"\n"
"Before you say anything, slowly breathe in and out five times. It will calm you, and give you a chance to think."
msgstr ""
"Tsala umoya ngokucothayo. Yima.\n"
"\n"
"Ngaphambi kokuba uthethe nantoni na, ngokucothayo tsala umoya uphinde uwukhuphe izihlandlo ezintlanu. Loo nto iya kukwenza uzole, ize ikunike ithuba lokucinga."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "SHARE"
msgstr "YABELANANI"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Share how you feel.\n"
"\n"
"This is hard. Many of us were told not to cry, or show our feelings to our children. But take a deep breath and calmly tell them how you feel. They will understand better, and also learn from you how to deal with stress."
msgstr ""
"Yabelana ngendlela ovakalelwa ngayo.\n"
"\n"
"Lento inzima. Uninzi lwethu lwaxelelwa ukuba lungakhali, okanye lubonise abantwana indlela esivakalelwa ngayo. Kodwa thatha umoya kwaye ngokuzolileyo ubachazele indlela ovakalelwa ngayo. Baya kuqonda ngcono, baze bafunde kuwe indlela yokuhlangabezana noxinzelelo."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "SHOW"
msgstr "BONISA"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Show them you care.\n"
"\n"
"This is also hard! Stress makes us focus on ourselves. But our teens need our support. Ask them how they feel. Listen to them and comfort them. Try a hug or say \"I understand\". It can change everything."
msgstr ""
"Babonise uyakhathala\n"
"\n"
"Nale inzima! Uxinzelelo lubangela ukuba sinikele ingqalelo kwiziqu zethu. Kodwa abantwana bethu abafikisayo bayayidinga inkxaso yethu. Babuze indlela abaziva ngayo. Mamela kubo kwaye ubathuthuzele. Zama ubanga okanye uthi ‚ÄòNdiyaqonda‚Äô. Ingatshintsha yonke into."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "SEEK"
msgstr "FUNA"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Seek the positive.\n"
"\n"
"Can you and your teen think about ideas that might help? Can you do something positive together to take your mind off the stress?"
msgstr ""
"Funa okulungileyo\n"
"\n"
"Ingaba wena nomntwana wakho ofikisayo ningacinga ngezinto ezinokuba luncedo? Ingaba nobabini ningenza into elungileyo ukususa iingqondo zenu kuxinzelelo?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"There are two home activities for this week:\n"
"\n"
"1) Whenever you are feeling stressed or upset with your teen, take five breaths in and out before you react.\n"
"And when you're both calm, share with each other how you feel. \n"
"\n"
"2) Choose a \"Safety Word\" with your teen, and think of a situation together when you could use this."
msgstr ""
"Kunemisebenzi emibini yasekhaya kule veki:\n"
"\n"
"1) Naninina uziva unoxinzelelo okanye ucatshukiswe ngumntwana wakho osafikisayo, tsala umoya kahlanu ngaphakathi nangaphandle phambi kokuba uphendule.\n"
"Kwaye xa nobabini nizolile, yabelanani kunye ngendlela eniziva ngayo.\n"
"\n"
"2) Khetha igama \"elikhuselekileyo\" kunye nomtana wakho ofikisayo, kwaye nicinge ngesimo kunye apho ninokwazi usebenzisa lento."

