#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Can you respond calmly and choose a ‚ÄúSafety Word‚Äù with your teen this week?"
msgstr "Ungakwazi uphendula ngokuzolileyo kwaye ukhethe \"Igama Elikhuselekileyo\" kunye nomntana wakho ofikisayo kuleveki?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Yes"
msgstr "Ewe"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Great! Staying calm and having a ‚ÄúSafety Word‚Äù will help you and your family."
msgstr "Kulungile! Ukuhlala uzolile kwaye \"unegama elikhuselekileyo\" izakunceda wena kunye nosapho lwakho."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "I think so"
msgstr "Ndicinga njalo"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "That‚Äôs a good start. When you are stressed, remember to take a few deep breaths, it will make it easier to respond calmly."
msgstr "Eso sisiqalo esilungileyo. Xa unoxinzelelo, khumbula ukutsala umoya kancinci, lonto izakwenza kubelula ukuphendula ngokuzolileyo."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "No"
msgstr "Hayi"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "I understand, sometimes we just don‚Äôt have capacity. Try to keep spending time with your teen - whenever you are ready you can practise responding calmly and find a Safety Word together."
msgstr "Ndiyayiqonda, ngamanye amaxesha asinawo umthamo. Zama uqhubeke uchitha ixesha nomntana wakho ofikisayo - naninina ulungele ungazilungiselela uphendula ngokuzolileyo kwaye ufumane igama elikhuselekileyo nobabini."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Remember, when we practice responding calmly and sharing how we feel, our teens learn to do the same. This skill will help them their whole life!"
msgstr "Khumbula xa siziqhelanisa ukuphendula zolileyo kwaye sabelane ngendlela esiziva ngayo, Abantwana bethu abafikisayo bafunda ukwenza ngohlobo esenza ngalo. Esisakhono siyakubanceda ubomu babo bonke!"

