msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Hear how @data.characters.media_son_1.name learned to stay calm from his father"
msgstr "Mamela indlela u@data.characters.media_son_1.name afunde ngayo ukuhlala ezolile kutata wakhe"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Whenever I would do something wrong, my father would get so angry at me and beat me. He would not even listen to me and I would get so angry as well at him and everyone else.\n"
"\n"
"Now, when he gets angry, he first takes a few deep breaths before he responds. It makes everyone calm down instead of causing a big fight.\n"
"\n"
"It really helped me at home and at school, because even me I am no longer slashing everyone and I am no longer this moody person. When I feel really angry or stressed, I also take deep breaths like my father does. I am a different person."
msgstr ""
"Naninina ndisenza into engalunganga, utata wam uye abenomsindo kakhulu kum kwaye andibethe. Akamameli nomamela kum kwaye ndiye ndibenomsindo kakhulu kuye nakwabanye abantu.\n"
"\n"
"Ngoku, Xa enomsindo utsala umoya kuqala kancinci phambi kokuba aphendule. Lonto yenza wonke umntu abenomoya ozolileyo ndaweni yokubangela umlo omkhulu.\n"
"\n"
"Iyandinceda nyani lonto ekhaya kunye nasesikolweni, kuba andisaphoxi wonke umntu kwaye andise ngomntu onengcwangu. Xa ndiziva ndinomsindo nyani kwaye ndinoxinzelelo, Nam nditsala umoya ngohlobo enza ngalo tata wam. Ndingumntu owohlukileyo."

